title: Please Help!
body: I'm in Silver 2 right now, I have difficulties in carrying my team and it seems like every lane feeds? No, this isn't the classic 'it's my teams fault I'm losing' because I know I should be able to carry them, but I'm looking for a duo partner to help me get to Gold before the Season ends.. Please help!

replies.body: Add up, also looking to Gold before season ends, please know that, I will want to play a norm with you before I start ranked, just to test out what your weaknesses are, and for you to know what mine are, so we can cover each other!
